<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0067a" xml:id="I01.0027.0067a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0067a01"/><cb:docNumber>No. 27</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0067a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>杜善勝等合邑七十人造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan><cb:div>
<pb n="0068a" xml:id="I01.0027.0068a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0068a0101">供養主佛□□　關退伽羅主杜善勝
<lb ed="I" n="0068a02"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a03"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a04"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a05"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a06"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a07"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a08"/>開明主齊承胤
<lb ed="I" n="0068a09"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a10"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a11"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a12"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a13"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a14"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a15"/>大齋主關退為亡父母亡兄
<lb ed="I" n="0068a16"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a17"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a18"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a19"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a20"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a21"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a22"/></p></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0068b" xml:id="I01.0027.0068b" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068b01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0068b0101">夫玄捴妙寂。炁末世<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0068001" n="0068001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0068001" n="0068001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0068001" n="0068001"/>所<anchor xml:id="end0068001"/>能顯
<lb ed="I" n="0068b02"/>其元。真景疑槨。非季俗之<anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="star"/>所<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068b03"/>宣其皇。是以鉢若之智難昇
<lb ed="I" n="0068b04"/>岨皆之葙。故<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0068002" n="0068002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0068002" n="0068002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0068002" n="0068002"/>顯<anchor xml:id="end0068002"/>神<g ref="#CB30521">󷜹</g>歸敬慈
<lb ed="I" n="0068b05"/>萇者矣。但聖藏淟澄洪<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">臨</unclear>道
<lb ed="I" n="0068b06"/>一炁可寶塔云重菒<g ref="#CB30522">󷜺</g>寶輻
<lb ed="I" n="0068b07"/>海臻。溸像寸暈則無牛号之
<lb ed="I" n="0068b08"/>潤<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0068003" n="0068003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0068003" n="0068003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0068003" n="0068003"/>哉<anchor xml:id="end0068003"/>。山岳摧巔。海獲崩竭。偘
<lb ed="I" n="0068b09"/>神儀於清流之曲。葵永顏不
<lb ed="I" n="0068b10"/>朽者也。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0068004" n="0068004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0068004" n="0068004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0068004" n="0068004"/>豈<anchor xml:id="end0068004"/>緣<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0068005" n="0068005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0068005" n="0068005"/><anchor xml:id="beg0068005" n="0068005"/>微<anchor xml:id="end0068005"/>工。當願正<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">備</unclear>。
<lb ed="I" n="0068b11"/>遠通慈<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0068006" n="0068006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0068006" n="0068006"/><anchor xml:id="beg0068006" n="0068006"/>朗<anchor xml:id="end0068006"/>。垢於<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0068007" n="0068007"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0068007" n="0068007"/><anchor xml:id="beg0068007" n="0068007"/>青<anchor xml:id="end0068007"/>宮。
<lb ed="I" n="0068b12"/>上為皇帝　陛下。國督祚康。
<lb ed="I" n="0068b13"/>祚幾標式。合右拙塢村。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">返</unclear>願
<lb ed="I" n="0068b14"/>合邑七十人等。敬造室家石
<lb ed="I" n="0068b15"/>像一區。直鍾薩提。願合邑<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0068008" n="0068008"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0068008" n="0068008"/><anchor xml:id="beg0068008" n="0068008"/>仰<anchor xml:id="end0068008"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068b16"/>隊七世。乃至<anchor xml:id="beg_2" type="star"/>所<anchor xml:id="end_2"/>生。朋<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0068009" n="0068009"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0068009" n="0068009"/><anchor xml:id="beg0068009" n="0068009"/>友<anchor xml:id="end0068009"/>眷屬。
<lb ed="I" n="0068b17"/>合霜奢梨。普洽私願。一時成
<lb ed="I" n="0068b18"/>佛。　　天寶二年保莊嚴功德飛騎尉杜思福邑子董
<lb ed="I" n="0068b19"/>建儀元年歲在毋申六月丁
<lb ed="I" n="0068b20"/>亥朔廿八日甲寅日
<lb ed="I" n="0068b21"/>願□主施□□</p></cb:div></cb:div>
